.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
City: liverpool, venice, rome, nizza, berlin
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: parkour, skateboarding, ice-hockey, lacrosse, surfing
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: orchid, begonia, amaryllis, balloon-flower, zinnia
The people use 5 different means of transport: motorbike, tram, roller, train, bus
The people have 5 different jobs:  designer, tramcher, social-worker, accountant, fisherman

1. the person who's sport is parkour is the person traveling to liverpool
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the designer
3. the person driving the motorbike is the person traveling to venice
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person driving the tram
5. the person traveling to venice is to the right of the person traveling to rome
6. the person who growsorchid is the fisherman
7. the person who growsbegonia is the person traveling to nizza
8. the person driving the roller is in the middle
9. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far left
10. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the tramcher
11. the person who growsbegonia is to the left or right of the accountant
12. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person driving the train
13. the person who's sport is surfing is the person who growszinnia
14. the person who's sport is lacrosse is to the left or right of the person traveling to berlin

